{"tid":2333720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普總統：戒嚴令是假新聞","createTime":"2020-12-20T15:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T16:05:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0acf87781727f191c0f474ab1e39470f8c4b7284","tid":2333720,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"目前很多川普總統的支持者呼籲總統實施戒嚴，但是川普總統週六發推說，「戒嚴令＝假新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1340523944680583169?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1340523944680583169%3Fs%3D20&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=125a472c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1340523944680583169%3Fs%3D20&h=0cfe529a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1340523944680583169?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n川普總統曾多次說，2020選舉是美國歷史上「最大的選舉欺詐」，並說拜登在6個搖擺州都輸了。<br />\n<br />\n他呼籲共和黨戰鬥到底，「 參院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾和共和黨參議員必須更加強硬，否則共和黨將不復存在。我們以很大的優勢贏得了總統大選。為它而戰。不要讓他們（民主黨人）奪走它！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/20/n12633433.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F12%2F20%2Fn12633433.htm&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=fe2c9d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/20/n12633433.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6c848624e5616e3217340deaea4d55a43506913a","tid":2333720,"uid":4722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"仲記得14號個日拜登夠270票<br />\n成班連登仔係到話咁內戰囉，咁軍管囉"}]}